{"\ufeff\n#  AgriPrime \u2014 MERN Stack Viva Preparation Guide \n> **Project:** AgriPrime \u2014 Unified Digital Platform for Agriculture & Livestock Management \n> **Stack:** MongoDB \u00b7 Express.js \u00b7 React.js \u00b7 Node.js \n> **Student Note:** The frontend (React) is fully implemented. The backend (MongoDB + Express + Node) is designed and ready for integration. \n--- \n##  Table of Contents \n1. [Project Overview](#1-project-overview) \n2. [MERN Architecture Diagram](#2-mern-architecture-diagram) \n3. [M \u2014 MongoDB (Database Layer)](#3-m--mongodb-database-layer) \n4. [E \u2014 Express.js (API Layer)](#4-e--expressjs-api-layer) \n5. [R \u2014 React.js (Frontend Layer)](#5-r--reactjs-frontend-layer) \n6. [N \u2014 Node.js (Server Runtime)](#6-n--nodejs-server-runtime) \n7. [Module-by-Module Breakdown](#7-module-by-module-breakdown) \n8. [Key Concepts Explained](#8-key-concepts-explained) \n9. [Anticipated Viva Questions & Answers](#9-anticipated-viva-questions--answers) \n10. [Tech Stack Summary Table](#10-tech-stack-summary-table) \n--- \n## 1. Project Overview \n**AgriPrime** is a unified digital platform that replaces manual record-keeping in Pakistani agriculture and livestock farms. It digitizes: \n| Module | Purpose | \n|--------|---------| \n|  Dashboard | Real-time overview of all farm KPIs | \n|  Livestock Management | Animal registration, RFID tracking, breed & health records | \n|  Veterinary & Breeding | Medical treatments, vaccination schedule, breeding calendar | \n|  Inventory & Feed Control | Stock levels, feed consumption, supplier orders | \n|  HR & Payroll | Employee profiles, task board, attendance, salary | \n|  Logistics & Delivery | Route planning, delivery tracking, dispatch records | \n|  Financial Tracking | Revenue (PKR), expenses, profit per animal category | \n|  Marketplace | E-commerce storefront for farm produce | \n|  Order Management | Customer orders, fulfillment, and status tracking | \n**Problem Solved:** Farmers previously used hand-written registers \u2014 data was lost, decisions were poor, and finances were untracked. \n\n--- \n## 2. MERN Architecture Diagram \n``` \n\u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u2502                        CLIENT (Browser)                          \u2502 \u2502  \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502              R E A C T . J S  (Vite)                       \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510  \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  \u2502App.jsx   \u2502 \u2502Dashboard \u2502 \u2502Livestock \u2502 \u2502  9 Screens   \u2502  \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  \u2502useState()\u2502 \u2502Component \u2502 \u2502Component \u2502 \u2502  Total       \u2502  \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518  \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  Routing via useState (SPA)  \u2502  HTTP fetch() / axios       \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u253c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518  \u2502 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u253c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \t \u2502 REST API Calls (JSON) \n\t \u2502 GET /api/livestock \n\t \u2502 POST /api/animals \n\t \u2193 \n\u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u2502                     SERVER (Node.js + Express.js)               \u2502 \u2502  \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  E X P R E S S . J S   REST API Server                  \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  app.js \u2014 Port 5000                                      \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502                                                           \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  Routes:                  Middleware:                     \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/animals             cors()                          \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/health-records      express.json()                  \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/employees           dotenv                          \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/inventory           morgan (logging)                \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/orders              JWT auth middleware             \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2502  /api/financial                                           \u2502    \u2502 \u2502  \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u252c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518    \u2502 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u253c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \t \u2502 Mongoose ODM \n\t \u2193 \n\u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u2502             M O N G O D B   (Database)                          \u2502 \u2502                                                                   \u2502 \u2502  Collections:                                                     \u2502 \u2502  \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510  \u2502 \u2502  \u2502 animals  \u2502 \u2502 employees \u2502 \u2502inventory \u2502 \u2502  orders          \u2502  \u2502 \u2502  \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518  \u2502 \u2502  \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510 \u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510                        \u2502 \u2502  \u2502 health   \u2502 \u2502 financial \u2502 \u2502logistics \u2502                        \u2502 \u2502  \u2502 records  \u2502 \u2502 records   \u2502 \u2502 routes   \u2502                        \u2502 \u2502  \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518                        \u2502 \u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518 ``` \n--- \n## 3. M \u2014 MongoDB (Database Layer) \n\n### What is MongoDB? \nMongoDB is a **NoSQL document database** that stores data as **JSON-like documents (BSON)** instead of rows and tables. It is schema-flexible and scales horizontally. \n> **Why MongoDB for AgriPrime?** \n> Farm data is diverse \u2014 an animal record has completely different fields from a financial record. MongoDB's flexible schema accommodates all modules without forcing a rigid relational table structure. \n--- \n### 3.1 Database: `agriprime_db` \n--- \n### 3.2 Collection: `animals` \nStores every livestock animal on the farm. \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('64f1c2a3b5e4d12a9c3f55ab')\", \t \"rfid\": \"RF-9921-A\", \n\t \"name\": \"Bessie 04\", \n\t \"species\": \"Cattle\", \n\t \"breed\": \"Black Angus\", \n\t \"gender\": \"Female\", \n\t \"dateOfBirth\": \"2021-06-12T00:00:00Z\", \n\t \"weightKg\": 580, \n\t \"status\": \"Healthy\", \n\t \"location\": \"Barn 4, Sector A\", \n\t \"purchaseDate\": \"2021-08-01T00:00:00Z\", \n\t \"purchasePricePKR\": 180000, \n\t \"owner\": \"ObjectId('64f1c2a3b5e4d12a9c3f0011')\", \t \"vaccinations\": [\"BVD\", \"FMD\", \"Anthrax\"], \n\t \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T08:00:00Z\", \n\t \"updatedAt\": \"2024-04-01T10:30:00Z\" \n} \n``` \n**Mongoose Schema:** \n```javascript \nconst animalSchema ": "new mongoose.Schema({ \n\t rfid:           { type: String, required: true, unique: true }, \t name:           { type: String, required: true }, \n\t species:        { type: String, enum: \n['Cattle','Sheep','Goat','Buffalo'], required: true }, \n\t breed:          String, \n\t gender:         { type: String, enum: ['Male','Female'] }, \n\t dateOfBirth:    Date, \n\t weightKg:       Number, \n\t status:         { type: String, enum: \n['Healthy','Sick','Quarantine','Sold','Deceased'], default: 'Healthy' }, \n\n\t location:       String, \n\t purchasePriceKPR: Number, \n\t vaccinations:   [String], \n}, { timestamps: true })", " \n``` \n--- \n### 3.3 Collection: `healthrecords` \nMedical history of each animal. \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\t \"animalId\": \"ObjectId('64f1c2a3b5e4d12a9c3f55ab')\", \t \"date\": \"2024-04-18T09:00:00Z\", \n\t \"diagnosis\": \"Mild Mastitis\", \n\t \"treatment\": \"Antibiotic injection \u2014 Oxytetracycline\", \t \"veterinarian\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\t \"followUpDate\": \"2024-04-25T00:00:00Z\", \n\t \"status\": \"Ongoing\", \n\t \"costPKR\": 4200 \n} \n``` \n--- \n### 3.4 Collection: `employees` \nFarm workers and their roles. \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\t \"name\": \"Fatima Malik\", \n\t \"cnic\": \"35202-1234567-8\", \n\t \"role\": \"Chief Veterinarian\", \n\t \"department\": \"Veterinary\", \n\t \"phone\": \"+92 300 1234567\", \n\t \"email\": \"fatima.malik@agriprime.pk\", \t \"salaryPKR\": 85000, \n\t \"status\": \"Active\", \n\t \"joiningDate\": \"2022-03-01T00:00:00Z\", \t \"location\": \"Bio-Lab 02\" \n} \n``` \n--- \n### 3.5 Collection: `inventory` \nFeed, medicines, and supplies. \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\n\t \"itemName\": \"Organic Corn Fodder\", \n\t \"category\": \"Feed\", \n\t \"quantityKg\": 2500, \n\t \"unitPriceKPR\": 80, \n\t \"reorderLevel\": 500, \n\t \"supplier\": \"Punjab Agri Suppliers\", \n\t \"warehouseLocation\": \"Godown A\", \n\t \"lastRestockedAt\": \"2024-04-07T08:00:00Z\" } \n``` \n--- \n### 3.6 Collection: `orders` \nE-commerce marketplace orders. \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\t \"orderNumber\": \"AP-2024-0042\", \n\t \"customer\": { \n\t\t \"name\": \"Ahmad Hassan\", \n\t\t \"phone\": \"+92 321 9876543\", \n\t\t \"city\": \"Lahore\" \n\t }, \n\t \"items\": [ \n\t\t { \"productName\": \"A-Grade Milk (5L)\", \"qty\": 4, \"unitPriceKPR\": 850 } \t ], \n\t \"totalAmountPKR\": 3400, \n\t \"status\": \"Processing\", \n\t \"paymentMethod\": \"JazzCash\", \n\t \"createdAt\": \"2024-04-07T14:22:00Z\" \n} \n``` \n--- \n### 3.7 Collection: `financialrecords` \n```json \n{ \n\t \"_id\": \"ObjectId('...')\", \n\t \"type\": \"Income\", \n\t \"category\": \"Milk Sale\", \n\t \"description\": \"A-Grade Milk Sale \u2014 Punjab Dairy Co.\", \t \"amountPKR\": 4210000, \n\t \"date\": \"2024-04-07T00:00:00Z\", \n\t \"relatedAnimalId\": null, \n\t \"relatedOrderId\": \"ObjectId('...')\" \n} \n``` \n--- \n\n### 3.8 MongoDB Key Concepts for Viva \n| Concept | Definition | AgriPrime Example | \n|---------|-----------|-------------------| \n| **Document** | A JSON-like record (row equivalent) | One animal's data | \n| **Collection** | Group of documents (table equivalent) | `animals` collection | \n| **ObjectId** | Auto-generated unique 24-char hex ID | `_id` field in every document | \n| **Schema** | Structure defined via Mongoose | `animalSchema` with field types & validation | \n| **Embedded Document** | Object nested inside a document | `customer` object inside `orders` | \n| **Reference** | ObjectId linking to another collection | `animalId` in `healthrecords` | \n| **Index** | Speeds up queries | Index on `rfid`, `status` in `animals` | \n| **Aggregation** | Pipeline to transform/group data | Sum revenue by animal category | \n| **timestamps** | Auto-adds `createdAt` / `updatedAt` | All schemas use `{ timestamps: true }` | \n--- \n## 4. E \u2014 Express.js (API Layer) \n### What is Express.js? \nExpress.js is a **minimal, unopinionated web framework for Node.js** that handles HTTP requests and builds REST APIs. \n> **Why Express?** It gives us full control over routing, middleware, and request handling with minimal boilerplate. \n--- \n### 4.1 Server Entry Point (`server.js`) \n```javascript \nconst express  ": "require('express')", " const mongoose ": "require('mongoose')", " const cors     ": "require('cors')", " \nconst dotenv   ": "require('dotenv')", " \ndotenv.config()": null, " \nconst app ": "express()", " \n// \u2500\u2500 Middleware \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 \napp.use(cors({ origin: 'http://localhost:5173' }))": null, "  // Allow React dev server \napp.use(express.json())": null, "                              // Parse JSON body app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: true }))": null, "     // Parse form data \n// \u2500\u2500 API Routes \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 \n\napp.use('/api/animals',   require('./routes/animalRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/health',    require('./routes/healthRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/employees', require('./routes/employeeRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/inventory', require('./routes/inventoryRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/orders',    require('./routes/orderRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/financial', require('./routes/financialRoutes'))": null, " app.use('/api/auth',      require('./routes/authRoutes'))": null, " \n// \u2500\u2500 MongoDB Connection \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 mongoose.connect(process.env.MONGO_URI) \n .then(() ": null, " \napp.listen(5000, () ": "> console.log(' AgriPrime Server running on port 5000'))", " \n``` \n--- \n### 4.2 Animal Routes (`routes/animalRoutes.js`) \n```javascript \nconst router  ": "require('express').Router()", " \nconst ctrl    ": "require('../controllers/animalController')", " const auth    ": "require('../middleware/authMiddleware')", " \n// GET all animals (with filters) \nrouter.get('/',      auth, ctrl.getAllAnimals)": null, " \n// GET single animal by ID \nrouter.get('/:id',   auth, ctrl.getAnimalById)": null, " \n// POST create new animal \nrouter.post('/',     auth, ctrl.createAnimal)": null, " \n// PUT update existing animal \nrouter.put('/:id',   auth, ctrl.updateAnimal)": null, " \n// DELETE remove animal \nrouter.delete('/:id',auth, ctrl.deleteAnimal)": null, " \n// GET animals by status \nrouter.get('/status/:status', auth, ctrl.getByStatus)": null, " \nmodule.exports ": "router", " \n``` \n--- \n### 4.3 Animal Controller (`controllers/animalController.js`) \n```javascript \nconst Animal ": "require('../models/Animal')", " \n\n// GET /api/animals \nexports.getAllAnimals ": null, "  // filter params \t\t const filter ": "{}", " \n\t\t if (breed)   filter.breed  ": "breed", " \n\t\t if (status)  filter.status ": "status", " \n\t\t if (species) filter.species ": "species", " \n\t\t const animals ": "await Animal.find(filter).sort({ createdAt: -1 })", " \t\t res.json({ success: true, count: animals.length, data: animals })": null, " \t } catch (err) { \n\t\t res.status(500).json({ success: false, message: err.message })": null, " \t } \n}": null, " \n// POST /api/animals \nexports.createAnimal ": null, " \n\t\t res.status(201).json({ success: true, data: animal })": null, " \n\t } catch (err) { \n\t\t if (err.code ": null, " \t\t } \n\t\t res.status(500).json({ message: err.message })": null, " \n\t } \n}": null, " \n// PUT /api/animals/:id \nexports.updateAnimal ": null, " \n\t\t if (!animal) return res.status(404).json({ message: 'Animal not found' })": null, " \n\t\t res.json({ success: true, data: animal })": null, " \n\t } catch (err) { \n\t\t res.status(500).json({ message: err.message })": null, " \n``` \n--- \n### 4.4 REST API Reference Table \n| Method | Endpoint | Description | Body | \n|--------|----------|-------------|------| \n| `GET` | `/api/animals` | Get all animals | \u2014 | \n\n| `GET` | `/api/animals/:id` | Get an